node.text:
Are you happy that for the very first time people are leaving California? Are you happy that the median price of a home is $800,000? Are you happy about homeless encampments? Are you happy about needles on Venice Beach? Are you happy about the education children are getting K-12? Are you happy that this state is running out of water? Are you happy with the fires? Are you happy that $30 billion was stolen from the Employment Development Department? Money that was supposed to be for unemployment for Californians. Are you happy with all of that?

If you're not, how about some change? How about some common sense? 

Vote YES to Recall Gavin Newsom.
